Aloha President Kouchi, Speaker Nakamura, and Members of the Legislature:
This is to inform you that on May 28, 2026, the following bill was signed into law:
H.B. NO. 469, H.D. 2, S.D. 2 RELATING TO PARKING FOR DISABLED
PERSONS.
